      <title>台风过后台湾有望恢复股票交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台风康蕾过境后，台湾准备恢复股票交易，但危险的风雨仍在继续，上海则准备迎接 1981 年以来 11 月份最强降雨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
